data.description: Lovely brick ranch in Cypress Shores with over a half-acre lot.  Enjoy relaxing on your large deck that overlooks a serene, fenced back yard.  A great location that is convenient to shopping centers, hospital and medical centers, and Historic Downtown New Bern.  This lovely home has many upgrades to include crown molding throughout the house.  The living room has a vaulted ceiling, ceiling fan, and gas fireplace.  The sellers also have natural gas available for the gas logs.  A pretty kitchen with ample storage has solid surface countertops, island, a sunny breakfast nook, and a walk-in pantry.   This home also has a formal dining room and new blinds throughout.  A large master suite has a walk-in closet, a nice soaking tub, separate shower, and a double vanity.  A great home with high quality.  Refrigerator in the kitchen does not convey; however, the refrigerator in the garage stays.
